ting delivery ethics (e.g., carbon footprint) under urgent demand spikes. By formalizing constraint violation as a negotiable, socially embedded process rather than a failure mode, ACN bridges the gap between safety-critical AI and adaptive autonomy, offering a scalable path toward trustworthy, flexible agents in open-world settings.",
